Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.57,0:01:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 雖然我搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不用特意跑去\N和志志雄那種人格鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種人不要理他就好了\N就這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛！\N人家擔心才跟你說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你死了有人會傷心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.99,0:02:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在東京的家人還有你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友當然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.27,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他一定會擔心現在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啦…\N因為我們是朋友 對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種戰鬥不要去打了 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到京都之後來我家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你吃很多好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再好好休息一下\N好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點走吧！緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 快一點\N朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道他們現在好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.51,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十八話\N左之助修行秘功！\N向破戒僧安慈的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 這下真的迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都在哪裏？畜生！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是這裏到底是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.57,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心那小子已經到京都了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐和彌彥\N也已經往京都出發了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠她…好不好？\N有很多病人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子當然也到京都去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這座森林 好像有印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太多心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 生氣肚子就餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一個\N再來就要抓青蛙來吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.77,0:04:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.75,0:04:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 是哪號人物？\N打攪別人吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是密教的修行僧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是什麼咒語？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.86,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是修行多年的和尚\N借用佛力所使出的法力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是迷路了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以麻煩你\N告訴我怎麼走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有吃的東西也給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這哪是向人要東西的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 因為我的修行\N讓饅頭掉到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關繫了\N因為那樣我才有這餐熱飯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又看到奇異的法力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是法力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法力 只是扇動世人信仰心的宣揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.68,0:05:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在佛門的我一次都沒見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真有的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我還不會用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚喝酒吃肉也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是破戒僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞僧！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 是破戒僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打破佛法戒律 墮落的和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N我看你的臉也不像做和尚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈可以貌取人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是既然捨棄佛家信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼又要在這裏修行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然捨棄了信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.56,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻沒有捨棄拯救世界的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.43,0:06:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且佛手並不能救世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有人的手才能拯救人世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的修行\N就是為了要得到那種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.57,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且\N那是凌駕在神佛之上的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:07:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該不會是輸給自已的慾望\N才變成破戒僧的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.95,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道十年前的排佛至釋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道的話 說了也是白說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不知道有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.06,0:07:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛的力量不是法力的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信心薄弱的我也可做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.21,0:07:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會拿去做壞事\N可不可以教我一點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼想要力量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚最會的禪問答嗎？\N有很多原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單來說是想比現在還要強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開東京的時候\N有和一個人打過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說我沒做到防禦的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.87,0:07:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微想了一下\N那不是我打鬥的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.34,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用我自己的方式變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你教教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修行也行 我什麼都肯做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣只想變強的人\N是叫做傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結論是沒有人\N可以忍耐我這種修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不去試怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下場終歸是送掉小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.93,0:08:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子做好小孩子就好了\N這也是為你自已好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.64,0:08:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要試試看\N我是不是還是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.72,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要力量\N我有需要力量的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你的救世比起來\N我的只是個人的理由而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但對我來說\N是個賭上性命的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再回答我一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.94,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得現今的明治政府怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？這有什麼關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說實話我不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不但殺了我師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還給他冠上叛賊的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能原諒他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這又有什麼關係呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你為了把這石頭打碎\N用拳頭打施以衝擊力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 不只是石頭\N所有的東西都會有抵抗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝擊力無法完全傳到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.87,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是會產生多餘的衝擊力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那多餘的衝擊力要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先\N握拳直直給石頭第一個擊力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後第一拳的衝擊\N在石頭的抵抗和擊中的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再正拳打出第二拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來\N第二拳就不會受到抵抗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.80,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊力完全傳到石頭就粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我修業十年悟出的\N破壞的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重極限…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應用這個\N剛剛我試的遠擊就可能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像非常簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆教我密訣好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼沒有粉碎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那只是速打兩拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝擊力是非常快速的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僅在那一瞬間 剎那的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在那瞬間擊出第二拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我悟出這秘訣後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.08,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花了一個月才練就破石粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要一個月練成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.16,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿你的性命來賭\N練不成就死在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重極限\N是為了救世而悟出的秘傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來就不是傳授給人的\N也不須廣為流傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有不服之處吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.54,0:11:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是破戒僧\N竟說出要拿人命的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 就賭命修練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒時間慢慢修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七天就要練成雙重極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 不怎麼順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.70,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續兩拳迅速的擊中石頭\N應該很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.47,0:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重極限沒那麼容易\N你終於瞭解了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一星期絕對不可能\N改變主意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做就會成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頑固的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.75,0:12:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才第三天而已\N距七天期限還有四天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.25,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做不做的到\N四天以後再做判斷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是在馬耳邊念佛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你罵誰是馬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還只是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好\N期限是一星期還剩下四天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時如果練不成雙重極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就按照約定納命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是賭命才能得到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當初我就不會要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的蠻力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重極限\N是我花了十年修行的結晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.47,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍有氣魄便會的話\N豈不太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離雙重極限還遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暈船的情形終於好多了嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是昏昏沉沉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這神谷活心流的技術\N會退步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 彌彥 那我就陪你練兩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.35,0:13:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰你也恢復精神了嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還太嫩了 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？現在才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他…他們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到神戶的外國人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,練不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.22,0:14:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣吧 這樣打下\N奇怪？是這樣吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就是約定的最後一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有…還有一個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有…天亮之前還有時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.11,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有…還有時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近的石頭都被我弄碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 只好去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 有時間卻沒有體力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.57,0:15:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恨 可恨\N我要葬身在這無名地嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在做夢 還是幻覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳…！沒有腳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再練了 左之助\N你已經盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經很拚命練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.77,0:16:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你認輸\N那男的還不至於要你的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.38,0:16:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣勉強的話\N你自已的命就不保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是隊長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時忘掉一切 今晚休息吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是隊長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法聽從這命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.71,0:16:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時我們赤報隊\N被冠上假軍官的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長被斬首後又被曝屍時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.02,0:17:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從心底憎恨維新政府\N也同樣的憎恨自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.03,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最尊敬的人被慘殺\N我卻什麼都不會無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恨死我自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經過了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位把我拉出沮喪的好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.81,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被捲入生死攸關的大戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想讓十年前那種悔恨\N再度重演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.72,0:17:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不准任何人讓它重演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我現在一定要變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少用這雙手\N擊碎所有不合理的暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是夢 還是幻覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是你的靈魂都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能再見到你我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竭力而死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人讓人有點惋惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.24,0:18:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少替他唸經…\N不要隨便殺人 和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是累了小睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.88,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你手上握著石頭\N想必還未練成雙重極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛才練成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:19:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一但抓住窮門\N這個小的就太輕鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是拼上一條命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.97,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸咎什麼才能\N不要輕描淡寫的一筆帶過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對 是我不好 重說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.79,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦！耽擱太多時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不趕緊去京都的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了中僊道\N再來就應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就太簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是下取訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.50,0:19:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了那邊的森林\N馬上就會到中僊道的驛站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下取訪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對的 怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.88,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪我覺得這森林很眼熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.09,0:19:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下取訪…\N不正是赤報隊終結的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在破壞僧的面前\N我這樣太失態了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.09,0:20:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開始有點相信弘佛的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝照顧 和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是相樂左之助\N有緣的話會再見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是悠久山安慈 路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.75,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子\N一晚之間改頭換面長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天以前還只是個小毛頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了 安慈我找了你好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始格鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.96,0:20:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄命令特攻部隊\N十本刀全體人員到京都集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到了 小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天到了大阪\N京都就近在眼前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就可抵達京都\N然後就能見到劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 你快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.55,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為爬過那座山頭\N很快就到京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺還有其他人都好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.83,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也難怪她會心急\N看來小操也很戀家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到家就是我的天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用坦白藥\N要他供出蒼紫的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經過了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本以為不會再到京都的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.61,0:21:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個地方\N正有一場戰鬥等著我

